Tell me your pick ? Guess I found my new favourite reds 🥰. Can you tell ? Swatched 4 shades from the gorgeous new @makeupforever Rouge Artist For Ever ❤️

•Here’s what stood out for me :

🪞An intensely pigmented formula that didn’t need a lipliner even for the first two Satin shades ! One swipe covers it all .
🪞The mattes are non drying ( the last two shades ) . 

🪞The case design looks stunning especially the glossy Satin. 

🪞The shape of the bullet is unique and helps with easy application . 

The only thing I’d change is the fragrance, a little strong for my nose .
